B019C062V005	19	62	5	I wait alone in silence for God;for from him comes my hope.
B019C062V006	19	62	6	Yes, he is my rock, my help, my retreat,I shall not be shaken too sorely.
B019C062V007	19	62	7	On God rests my honour and safety,in God is my strong rock, my refuge.
B019C062V008	19	62	8	Trust in him, all you people assembled,pour out your heart in his presence;God is a refuge for us.  (Selah)  
