B019C066V006	19	66	6	He turns the sea into dry land,and people cross the river on foot.Let us therefore rejoice in him,
B019C066V007	19	66	7	the mighty Ruler eternal,whose eyes keep watch on the nations,that no rebel lift up his head.  (Selah)  
B019C066V008	19	66	8	O bless our God, you peoples;sound aloud his praise,
B019C066V009	19	66	9	who keeps us in life,and keeps our feet from slipping.
