B019C078V013	19	78	13	Through the sea which he split he brought them,making waters stand up like a heap;
B019C078V014	19	78	14	he led them by day with a cloud,all the night with a light of fire. 
B019C078V015	19	78	15	From the rocks which he split in the wilderness,he gave them to drink as of ocean’s abundance.
B019C078V016	19	78	16	He brought streams out of the rock,and made water run down like rivers. 
