B019C078V033	19	78	33	So he ended their days in a breath,and their years in sudden dismay.
B019C078V034	19	78	34	When he slew them, then they sought after him,they turned and sought God with diligence. 
B019C078V035	19	78	35	They remembered that God was their rock,and the Most High God their redeemer.
B019C078V036	19	78	36	But they flattered him with their mouth,and lied to him with their tongue.
B019C078V037	19	78	37	Their heart was not steady with him,they were faithless to his covenant. 
