B041C015V027	41	15	27	And with him they crucified two robbers, one on the right, and the other on the left.  
B041C015V029	41	15	29	The passers-by railed at him, shaking their heads, as they said: “Ah! You who would destroy the Temple and build one in three days,
B041C015V030	41	15	30	come down from the cross and save yourself!”
