B043C003V030	43	3	30	He must become greater, and I less.”
B043C003V031	43	3	31	He who comes from above is above all others; but a child of earth is earthly, and his teaching is earthly, too. He who comes from heaven is above all others.
B043C003V032	43	3	32	He states what he has seen and what he heard, and yet no one accepts his statement.
